{"TopicId":154876,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"SOLVED: Inverted controls and NavBall after reverting flight to launch and pressing the M key","CreatedByName":"WAKSLOB","CreatedById":130651,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T11:52:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"WAKSLOB","CreatedById":130651,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T11:52:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI made a video demonstrating my issue here below.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/aE7K8dXL3es\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-14T05:43:45Z\u0022 title=\u002201/14/2017 05:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 14, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by WAKSLOB\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ESolved\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T11:56:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis happened to me once. I just saved the game and restarted KSP. It seemed to fix it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WAKSLOB","CreatedById":130651,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T12:04:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI restarted my game like u\u00A0suggested\u00A0but still the same behavior.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T15:47:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222918976\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221484222644\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130651\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WAKSLOB\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, WAKSLOB said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI restarted my game like u\u00A0suggested\u00A0but still the same behavior.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell in that case I\u0027m sorry. Ask \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002216426\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/16426-sal_vager/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@sal_vager\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0or one of the other moderators for help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T15:53:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout having your craft file this is a guess, but your root part may be inverted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T16:14:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222919199\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221484236385\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002216426\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sal_vager\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, sal_vager said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout having your craft file this is a guess, but your root part may be inverted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAbout 99.99% sure this is the correct answer. Just yesterday the exact same thing happened to me. I RARELY place a root part upside down but it this case I did. And it inverted the navball on reverts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-12T16:14:42Z\u0022 title=\u002201/12/2017 04:14  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 12, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Tex_NL\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WAKSLOB","CreatedById":130651,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T05:42:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222918962\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221484222171\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo Var Lachland\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/12/2017 at 6:56 AM, Lo Var Lachland said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis happened to me once. I just saved the game and restarted KSP. It seemed to fix it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the sake of the interwebz, i found the problem. \u00A0I had to right click my command module and click \u0022Take control\u0022\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-14T14:58:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222921034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022154876\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221484372560\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130651\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WAKSLOB\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, WAKSLOB said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the sake of the interwebz, i found the problem. \u00A0I had to right click my command module and click \u0022Take control\u0022\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh yes, THAT. Sorry I\u00A0didn\u0027t mention it. I just remembered that thats what I did. Sorry dude.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmay your rockets fly safe and straight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n~Lo\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}